Taskify Ninja Privacy Policy

Welcome to Taskify Ninja! Your privacy is of utmost importance to us. At Taskify Ninja, we are dedicated to safeguarding your personal information and ensuring a positive experience on our application. This Privacy Policy outlines how we handle and protect your personal information within the Taskify Ninja mobile application ("App").

1. Data Collection and Usage

Taskify Ninja is designed with your privacy in mind. We do not collect, store, or process any personal data or information from our users. This includes any information that could be used to identify, contact, or locate an individual, either on its own or when combined with other information. Additionally, no personal information is gathered during the use of our application.

2. Legal Basis for Processing

Since Taskify Ninja does not collect or process any personal data, the typical legal bases for processing personal data under various data protection laws, such as GDPR, do not apply to our app.

3. User Rights

Given that we do not collect any personal data, the rights typically afforded to users under data protection laws, such as GDPR's rights to access, rectification, erasure, restrict processing, object to processing, and data portability, are not applicable in the context of our app. However, we support and advocate for the protection of privacy rights globally.

4. Data Security

Taskify Ninja is committed to ensuring the security of our users. As we do not collect any personal information, there are no risks of your personal data being lost, misused, accessed, disclosed, altered, or destroyed by our app.

5. Third-Party Services

Taskify Ninja does not utilize any third-party services. Our application operates solely on its own infrastructure and does not require any external services or data transfers.

6. Changes

The Taskify Ninja Privacy Policy may be updated and modified periodically. Any changes will be made with the knowledge and, if necessary, consent of the users. Therefore, we recommend periodically reviewing our Privacy Policy.

7. Contact

If you have any questions, concerns, or feedback, please do not hesitate to contact us. For any inquiries regarding our privacy policy or our application, you can email us at euphranos238@gmail.com.

This Privacy Policy was last updated on 08.04.2024.
